Author: amooni95
Text: My stomach always rats me out to my already-concerned bf. "What did you eat today? ðŸ¤¨" "nothing yet, been busy and haven't gotten around to eating yet." Just yesterday he texted me "No babe I do get it but I also believe theses a direct link from your stomach to your mind." after I told him he just doesn't understand and that it's not as simple as "just don't fast."
